In 2020 , fertility rates at age 25-29 years for Dominican Republic was 162.34 births per 1,000 women . Between 1975 and 2020 , fertility rates at age 25-29 years of Dominican Republic was declining at a moderating rate to shrink from 286.72 births per 1,000 women in 1975 to 162.34 births per 1,000 women in 2020 .

In 2019 , male admission rates in infections and parasitic diseases in Malaysia was 502 cases per 100,000 population . Male admission rates in infections and parasitic diseases in Malaysia fell gradually from 653 cases per 100,000 population in 2009 to 502 cases per 100,000 population in 2019 .

In 2018 , private car theft rate for Nepal was 24.3 cases per 100,000 populations . Private car theft rate of Nepal increased from 12.9 cases per 100,000 population in 2016 to 24.3 cases per 100,000 population in 2018 growing at an average annual rate of 50.14 % .
